Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, a rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, it's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A rainbow?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.69,0:00:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, you played mahjong all night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I had to!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the game of a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We gambled with Youko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s precious photos!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that was something that required you to go to the hot springs?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.51,0:00:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is magic, attack the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:53.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On Saturday nights, be sure to click on Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has a clear view but it's prone to accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.15,0:00:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the diabolical intersection, a tiny suspicion surfaces!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.38,0:00:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, go check on that car!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't save him like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, how is it over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:21.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't get the door open!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, both of these cars stopped at the\Nconvenience store a while ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:36.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:39.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... gu... ess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like you were in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:48.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the other car?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:50.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to help him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the car was on fire and I can't go near it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, call an ambulance and the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:01.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did this happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:19.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a huge accident I've caused...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've caused something irreversible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, well, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:30.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks... but I don't smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were driving the green car, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have some questions to ask, will that be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:45.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, your name and occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:51.72,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(0,0)}Kurumatani Seiji (28)\N{\fs12}Auto Mechanic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:51.72,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm Kurumatani Seiji, an auto mechanic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you're the primary witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:55.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, so you're the famous detective Mouri Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard a lot about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, it's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's that Mouri Kogorou?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:13.61,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(0,0)}Michida Junko (38)\N{\fs12}Okuho Police Dept, Traffic Division Patrol Officer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:13.61,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm so honored to have such a\Nfamous detective here to help us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you were the first to discover\Nthe two cars involved in the accident, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the red car was already on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The driver, Hayami Shun{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, was confirmed dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kurumatani{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me what happened during the accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was entering the intersection...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I didn't notice the other car approaching at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I kept driving straight ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, red car suddenly entered my line of sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I slammed my brakes and turned my steering wheel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still couldn't avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before you entered the intersection, did you not stop for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I neglected to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the accident happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:05.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The iron bars are severely bent...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This car...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has a front grill guard installed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you said about the other car suddenly\Ncoming into sight is unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you actually dozed off or looked elsewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:27.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I looked in front of me and drove as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:32.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just didn't notice the other car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:33.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This intersection is in the middle of an\Nopen field and you had a clear view!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:42.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is notorious for being accident-prone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Locals have even nicknamed it the "Intersection of Fear."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Intersection of Fear," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:59.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to one theory, the "collision course\Nphenomenon" may play a role in this type of accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That "college course phenomenon"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's "collision course phenomenon."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even during the daytime and with a clear view\Nof the intersection, accidents may still occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If two cars approach the same intersection at the same speed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They will constantly stay at a 45 degree angle relative to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the other car will always be in\Nthe same spot of the driver's outer visual field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although humans have both central and peripheral vision...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to detect tiny movements with only our peripheral vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might take too much time to finally notice the other car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, it's already too late when the cars come\Nup on the intersection, and a collision is inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:51.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Kurumatani{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s accident was caused by this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Collie-show course phenomenon"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's "collision course", you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:07:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think that was why the accident happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe there's such a phenomenon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:07.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I had paid more attention, this wouldn't have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't any brake marks coming from the red car at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.67,0:08:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other driver in the red car didn't\Nnotice the incoming traffic either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:26.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "collision course phenomenon"\Nexplanation becomes all the more plausible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, in a wide field such as this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both drivers still couldn't notice each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't accept that so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you're a private detective, it's second\Nnature for you to doubt everything, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two cars we saw at the convenience store are all smashed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:46.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were both cars at the convenience store?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I stopped to buy canned coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:09:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw the two cars leave the parking lot around the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:07.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you think about it, this is too coincidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two cars departed at the same time, but drove on different roads...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A few minutes later, they crashed into each other here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that merely a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was a coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be safe, shall we go check with the convenience store?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:34.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came around 2:00PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had quite an attitude so it bothered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir, did you come yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out there, I think I remember seeing that green car of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That belongs to that bastard, Kurumatani!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't mix things up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He snapped at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He really mentioned "Kurumatani," you're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:09:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That makes Hayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} an acquaintance of Kurumatani{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew something was fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This person...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was the one who was quarrelling with the young man earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time we saw the two cars leave, it was\Nafter those two had finished their fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crash happened shortly after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall, at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kurumatani{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were actually acquaintanced with\NHayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who drove that foreign red car, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen his face before, but I don't know if I'd call us acquaintances.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:19.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what were you arguing about with\NHayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at the convenience store?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The store manager witnessed what happened between you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, about that red foreign car...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was sold by a friend at a used car company three months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that the customer who bought it wasn't\Npaying his loans, so I tried to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:38.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he snapped at me, and it turned into a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, why did you drive this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your residence should be in the opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:53.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just... I had extra time to spare, so I drove around to chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:56.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rainbow was beautiful, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rainbow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:12:00.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there a rainbow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why all these questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They have nothing to do with the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kurumatani{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you're an auto mechanic, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, and?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, you already knew that this place is prone to car accidents!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you argued with him at the store...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:28.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You rigged his brakes while Hayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nwent shopping for a few minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be a piece of cake for a mechanic like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:35.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was why there were no brake marks from that red foreign car!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, we didn't find any abnormalities\Nfrom the red car's braking system.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you must've jammed something under his brake pedal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's done often to disguise accidents!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did that because you wanted to teach Hayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, to your surprise, this caused a\Nserious accident and Hayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you had to pretend\Nyou knew nothing, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we didn't discover anything suspicious inside that red car either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective, please don't come up with strange stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, don't smoke in the open!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an ashtray inside the car, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car ashtray?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:53.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What were you doing, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've prepared the footage from the surveillance camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:14:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a surveillance camera at this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because there are so many accidents around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:05.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No kids allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The red car entered the intersection without hitting the brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the green car smashed into it soon after.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the green car crashed into the billboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the red car fell into the ditch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that this was merely an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:44.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really want a look at that footage...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:46.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you wander around again, Dad's gonna get get angry at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:56.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:00.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:03.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:10.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad said so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:25.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like it was a normal accident, just as you testified.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:36.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, I'm holding you responsible for not stopping before entering.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.86,0:15:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like the case is closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you then, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take your statement regarding the accident at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:54.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:16:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:04.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is no ordinary accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a premeditated...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:10.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:15.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kurumatani{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said he coincidentally met\NHayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:17.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boy from my agency just checked out your car ashtray.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were many cigarette butts inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.16,0:16:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:33.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you don't smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The brand of the cigarettes is Paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:42.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there are bite marks on the cigarette filters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:44.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same as the one at the convenience store's parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The smoked cigarette tossed by Hayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, on the way to the convenience store,\NHayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was actually driving the green car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:17:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps while you serviced Hayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s red foreign car at\Nyour repair shop, you lent him the green car as a loaner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:14.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you serviced it, you called him to that convenience store\Nto exchange his car with your green loaner, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:18.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you murdered Hayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, disguising it as a car accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, Kurumatani{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} planned to\Ncrash his own car into Hayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm injured, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:34.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without some luck, I could've died as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:37.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had no reason to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because your car...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was protected by a sturdy front grill guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:48.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You planned to injure yourself a little, so the\Naccident would look all the more convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:50.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just bluffing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was an accident caused by the collision course phenomenon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other car didn't hit its brakes at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the best evidence, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I think it's hard for people to manipulate this phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason why Hayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't hit the brakes\Nwasn't due to the collision course phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kurumatani{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} deployed a trick to disable\NHayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} from hitting the brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They just said nothing was suspicious in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:26.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trick was placed at a different place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:28.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is a billboard covered with a light-reflective\Nsheet, like they do with traffic signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's usually facing the direction Hayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had approached from.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you shine light on the billboard, there will be a resulting glare.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The glare does strain the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that Kurumatani{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} adjusted the\Nposition that the billboard faced beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, Hayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would be blinded by the\Nbillboard reflecting sunlight directly into his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't we notice that when we\Nwere watching the camera footage?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:15.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was outside the camera's range, so it wasn't caught on tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After leaving the convenience store, Hayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s car was\Nmoving alongside the ditch, approaching this intersection.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because he had the right-of-way over other traffic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't slow down, and drove straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By then, the billboard had been adjusted so that the reflected\Nsunlight would shine right before the intersection.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without knowing this, Hayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} drove straight into the intersection...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was blinded by the glare,\Nand couldn't hit the brakes in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And because of the afterimage caused by the light\Ninterfering with his eyes, he couldn't see your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You chose to meet at the convenience store at 2:00PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you calculated beforehand\Nwhere the glare would shine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, the reason he crashed into the billboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was to hide the fact he adjusted the board's direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:26.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And perhaps the reason you crashed into\NHayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s driver seat was also...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I planned to run straight into him, crushing him to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:37.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hayami was the culprit who ran over my\Nlittle sister with his car one year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Half a year ago, I recognized the foreign red\Ncar that came to my shop for maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, all I could think about was revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then Hayami brought his car in for maintenance again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was when I planned this whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:21:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I returned his car, I asked him to turn himself over to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he acted like he didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when I proceeded with my plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he had turned himself in, I would've spared his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet you kept quiet about killing Hayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nand disguising it as an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the same kind of coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's now your turn to turn yourself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective, when did you realize that I planned this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you said you didn't remember seeing a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.89,0:21:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The collision course phenomenon requires\Nthe driver to face straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:46.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason you didn't notice a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.15,0:21:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it because all you thought about was crashing into\NHayami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s car, meaning you only looked to the side?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you let anger and revenge consume you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:22:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll find yourself unable to behold the\Nbeautiful sights right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, speeding while you're sleepy is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.59,0:23:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel refreshed somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should, since I put you to sleep earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.68,0:23:41.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't return this car tonight, they're\Ngonna charge us an extra rental fee!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.14,0:23:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would cost much more if you get into an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.72,0:23:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're fine, we're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.93,0:23:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, we're gambling for Youko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s\Npremiere DVD in our mahjong tournament tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.48,0:23:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Youko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:57.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the "Kogorou-never-learns phenomenon" for you.
